://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}, {\"begin\": 4598, \"end\": 4607, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9999031347434765, \"rank\": 9.687464026184058e-05, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"so many people\", \"from\": 4528, \"to\": 4542}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Those people need to hear the gospel too.\", \"from\": 4639, \"to\": 4680, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Those people\", \"from\": 4639, \"to\": 4651}, {\"ngram\": \"the gospel\", \"from\": 4665, \"to\": 4675}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's the ones that are lukewarm about it that may think like, 'Ah - I do not want to ruffle any feathers.\", \"from\": 4681, \"to\": 4786, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ones\", \"from\": 4686, \"to\": 4694}, {\"ngram\": \"any feathers\", \"from\": 4773, \"to\": 4785}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Live and let live.\", \"from\": 4787, \"to\": 4805, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Let people do what they want.\", \"from\": 4806, \"to\": 4835, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 4810, \"to\": 4816}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am just gonna stay in my corner and be quiet about it.'\\\"\", \"from\": 4836, \"to\": 4894, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my corner\", \"from\": 4860, \"to\": 4869}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the Hallmark star stopped short of calling for a boycott.\", \"from\": 4896, \"to\": 4957, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4904, \"end\": 4912, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hallmark_Channel\", \"score\": 0.9999999895444489, \"rank\": 1.0449577660078318e-08, \"text\": \"Hallmark\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hallmark_Channel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hallmark_Channel\"}], \"noun_phrases\